text: The New Taipei Municipal Hsing Wu High School () is a secondary school in Linkou District, New Taipei, Taiwan. ==History== Ku Huai-tsu (" 從無到有，醒吾奮鬥的歷程." Hsing Wu High School. Retrieved on November 27, 2012.) founded the school in 1963. The school's first class had 113 students. The school was fully established in 1969."English." Hsing Wu High School. June 27, 2007.
